<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6987307>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Overbeckia papuana sp. nov. holotype (worker) and its lateral (a), frontal (b) and dorsal (c) views. Detail of head sculpture and shape of frontal carinae (d)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6987307/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6987309>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Overbeckia papuana sp. nov. paratypes (alates). Queen: lateral (a), dorsal (c) and frontal (e) views; male: lateral (b), dorsal (d) and frontal (f) views. Note that the petiole in queen (a) looks wider and blunter due to being bent to the right site (c)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6987309/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

